title: It Got Plenty Awkward When This BBC Commentator Mistook a Random Woman Walking Out of the White House for Michelle Obama
text:
It Got Plenty Awkward When This BBC Commentator Mistook a Random Woman Walking Out of the White House for Michelle Obama Jerry Thornton | Email 
Live TV moments don’t get any more cringeworthy than this. But in fairness, when you spent your entire career as a reporter doing non-stop fake news coverage of a royal family who live in a pretend fairy tale world, real political families with actual power probably confuse and frighten you. Still, if an American news anchor did this, they’d be off the air by the next commercial break. But these are Brits we’re talking about. I’m sure all White House employees look alike to them. Jerry Thornton |
